  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game contains flashes of light that can cause epileptic seizures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A psychological horror - <strong>Inside Intruder</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First person</strong> horror with retro graphics. Where u need to navigate through the house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mild discomforting sounds throughout the entire game and only<strong> YOUR</strong> choices lead you to your desired path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It's easy</i> <i>right</i> ?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>WELL....</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Intruder is <strong>inside</strong>. All he wants is your suffering.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404050/extras/6891fd20285c45d6a1a03eff4ca4926d.poster.avif?t=1735726504\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404050/extras/6891fd20285c45d6a1a03eff4ca4926d.webm?t=1735726504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404050/extras/6891fd20285c45d6a1a03eff4ca4926d.mp4?t=1735726504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a kid home ALONE.<i> Waiting for his parents to come home, but do you want them to join you ?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore all the <strong>6</strong> <strong>unique</strong> endings and <strong>beat</strong> the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The alternate is in the air, don't breathe u may accidently reveal your fear.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game contains flashes of light that can cause epileptic seizures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A psychological horror - <strong>Inside Intruder</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First person</strong> horror with retro graphics. Where u need to navigate through the house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mild discomforting sounds throughout the entire game and only<strong> YOUR</strong> choices lead you to your desired path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It's easy</i> <i>right</i> ?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>WELL....</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Intruder is <strong>inside</strong>. All he wants is your suffering.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404050/extras/6891fd20285c45d6a1a03eff4ca4926d.poster.avif?t=1735726504\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404050/extras/6891fd20285c45d6a1a03eff4ca4926d.webm?t=1735726504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404050/extras/6891fd20285c45d6a1a03eff4ca4926d.mp4?t=1735726504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a kid home ALONE.<i> Waiting for his parents to come home, but do you want them to join you ?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore all the <strong>6</strong> <strong>unique</strong> endings and <strong>beat</strong> the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The alternate is in the air, don't breathe u may accidently reveal your fear.</p>",
